# SHError.Code.mediaItemFetchFailed

**Case**

The error code to indicate when the system fails to fetch one or more media items.

## Declaration

```swift
case mediaItemFetchFailed
```

## Library sync errors

- **SHError.Code.mediaLibrarySyncFailed**: The error code to indicate when the system fails to add one or more media items to the user’s Shazam library.
